@startuml
'https://plantuml.com/sequence-diagram

autonumber

title Register an Airport: Simplified Sequence Diagram

actor "Backoffice Operator" as BO
participant ":System" as S

BO -> S: Asks to register an Airport
S --> BO: Requests Airport Details \n(String name, LocationIdentifier iata, Coordinates coordinates,\n AirportLocation airport_location, AirportType airport_type, List<RunwayInfo> runway_info,\n AirportStatus status, TimeZone time_zone, OperationalHours operational_hours,\n List<ContactInfo> contact_info, List<AirportTerminal> terminals, List<AirportGate> gates,\n List<AirportService> services, List<String> images)

BO -> S: Types requested data
S --> BO: Shows all data and requests confirmation

BO -> S: Confirms the data
S --> BO: Registers the Airport and informs operation success

@enduml